description:
In this episode we discover the disciples of Jesus and their importance. Jesus chose a group of disciples to work with him - something that would probably have been overlooked by many other teachers. However, he saw something in them that he could work with. Despite lacking experience and education, he saw willingness and humility, and that was more important than anything else.
